Yes, they're new.

292
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:19,310
They're slow in their work.

293
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:23,790
Come with me.

294
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,640
There's still a lot of work.

295
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,200
Alright, get back to your work.

296
