316
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,310
Yes, we'll get going now.

317
00:20:26,790 --> 00:20:28,590
It's the crown prince.

318
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:29,830
That's great.

319
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:31,200
Thank God for that.

320
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,240
My plan is perfect now.

321
