someone in the bucket.

328
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,880
We should be out of the camp soon.

329
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:41,070
Victory is in sight.

330
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,200
There are people in the buckets.

331
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:57,550
