375
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:25,400
is making private weapons
and training his own soldiers.

376
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:27,680
The crown prince is now investigating

377
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:30,200
in the Wei family's weapons camp.

378
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:32,200
