379
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:34,830
Your Majesty, please make a decision
as soon as possible

380
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,960
to save two princes from danger.

381
00:24:43,750 --> 00:24:44,480
Your Highness,

382
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:45,960
all of the spies

383
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:46,880
