451
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,070
No one can hurt her.

452
00:27:14,350 --> 00:27:15,480
Calm down.

453
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,160
Is it worth

454
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:19,030
